Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.14,Top,,0,0,0,,How much longer?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.50,Top,,0,0,0,,About four minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tricky, Fukuda-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.83,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan is a developed country and one of the world's leaders,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.43,0:01:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yet within its territory there is an island that remains closed to the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, Champon Kingdom, I know. {ちゃんぽん王国}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.00,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, there's that boy—\Ncarrying a sword, wearing a topknot,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and still thinking it's the age of samurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.12,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it wouldn't make a good look \Nif other countries find out.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.13,0:01:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, not a good look at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the laughingstock of the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.68,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I need you to do, \NVice-Minister Fukuda...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You go there!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Foreign Minister,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.61,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that island seems to be inhabited \Nby all sorts of weird creatures.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know of. \NNo such report has ever been filed.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.76,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, I heard that it's untouched nature is a sight to see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.32,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you were worried about your son, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should bring him along.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, do just that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.19,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad it doesn't have any golf courses, it seems.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not too bored!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast! Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to go to that island?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, it's observable now. {**satsukan = some kind of inspector, I assume they call him that because he's inspecting it?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Champon Kingdom.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It's but a tiny island!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they call that Champon Kingdom?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.90,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's that childish shape anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.45,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I can see some weird statue.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Lemme see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.46,0:02:50.95,Top,,0,0,0,,What on earth is that? Such a weird structure!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.07,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some moyai-like guy standing on one foot \Nwith a tanuki pouring liquor on top of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.57,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And further up, something incomprehensible with a silly face puffing out clouds of smoke?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the guardian \Nof the island or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those islanders are an idiosyncratic bunch. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! There's something's approaching!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.59,Top,,0,0,0,,Funny machine! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a child...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it has wings... {??? it actually doesn't but maybe he concluded that because he can fly?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Jiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.04,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pester that thing! \NHurry up and come down! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.74,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... It's my dad! \NComing up now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.71,0:03:45.99,Top,,0,0,0,,Jiro, if you don't hurry, \Nyou'll be late for your Shichigosan Ceremony. {shichi-go-san; 7-5-3 day; festival day for children aged 7, 5 and 3 held on or around November 15 - terrible adaptation, but shichigosan simply doesn't have a translation succinct enough; funny I've encountered this concept in two projects in a row}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What, what are these guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to my Shichigosan Ceremony!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.60,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? What's with this island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,100,,Sensei! I am grateful for the training! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.11,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibo Takamaru, 11 years old—\Nheading to school!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Acorns?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow, Takamaru! {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I ride that too! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged, Mirai-dono!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! You've gotta punish this jerk! \NHe jumped me for no reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NIt was you who brought a gun!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You beget chaos wherever you go. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.67,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibo Takamaru, Yumega Al Zaemon{夢我アル佐ェ門},\Nwhy don't I just leave you hanging there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.65,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Please wait for me, Mirai-dono! \NI don't wanna be late to school!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I'm Al! \NDon't call me Al Zaemon!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must cherish the name you received from your parents, Yumega Al Zaemon!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.18,0:08:41.60,Top,,0,0,0,,G-Goddamn! I'm Al! I don't want a lame name like Al Zaemon! {lit: no to name}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Al, don't you think it's not the time to talk about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I kept you waiting, \NFukuda-dono!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get a good sleep last night?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.55,Top,,0,0,0,,This here is the king of our beloved country,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.92,Top,,0,0,0,,Zako Takanokami Kaodeka.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Fukuda Fukutaro, \Nsent to inspect your small island
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on behalf of Japan's Ministry of Foreign Affairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Small island?!" \NHow rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.63,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Small as it may be, our Champon Kingdom \Nis a splendid independent country!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.63,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no grounds \Nto consider us Japan's territory!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Legal status discussions always take time, so let's take it slowly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, my son Claude \Nis nowhere to be seen...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I took your son to our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-School?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.58,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But my son hasn't been to school \Nin six months now...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.05,0:10:13.80,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is he one of those famous \NJapanese school truants? {登校拒否}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.80,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way for boys and girls \Nto learn and play is together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.76,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Claude is enjoying his gym class \Nwith everyone right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! The white team is behind, \Nbut it's catching up fast! {?????? nc what's that atoushiro}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, both of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.00,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All, right, it's my turn! \NYou, the City Boy! Take care of the rest here! {?????? nc what's that tokaemon}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold medal for me! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then, Claude, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.04,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes! Claude, do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly, white team! \NDon't let him win! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru-san will overtake him now!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Claude-dono? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's wrong? \NAnyone can do that jump!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do \Nsomething this incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible? You mean this obstacle course?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.38,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! There's something wrong with you all \Nif you can do that so easily!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there! It's hiding there!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.89,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Got a big one!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Found another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the shadow of this stone!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole three of them here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy, Takamaru! \NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, it's yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.78,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn't Takamaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.63,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You lot are wasting your time \Nwith toddlers again? {to loiter (on the way); to waste time}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not come home sooner \Nand help with housework?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks who's talking!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.35,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't exactly making the best use of your time either! {lit: wasting time on the way as parent and child}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, City Boy, what's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not loitering around, Al.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.92,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here on a duty to escort the son \Nof an important inspector from Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Such a simple mission \Nfor the king's spy? {spy working for the Edo shogunate; oniwaban}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be important.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let me...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this, this, and then this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Goshdarn... \NIt exploded!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle! \NHow did you do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.71,0:14:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, anyone can do that if the sensor \Nof the robot matches the laser of the pistol.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell knows what you just said, \Nbut it sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.74,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, and there... \NAnd now... Finish!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be damned! \NYou are genius!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it felt like you were \Nthat guy yourself! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What... What's that thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hell knows what it is, \Nbut it's always been there. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When it does that, \Nit means the children should go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, it's time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.70,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, why don't you be friends with Claude while he's in our country?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask \Nfor something like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude, won't you rent this toy to me again if we're friends? {lit: make it rental}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I'll be staying here for long.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So then you'll be taking \Nthe toys with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave them to you \Nwhen it's time to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! That's OK with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be your friend from now on!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to leave your toys to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.86,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.71,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Al Zaemon, can he really call you a "friend?" {probably means "is it friendship if it's for material interest"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it to you?! \NWe're already friends, you hear? Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, when people hang out together...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, OK, OK, OK, I heard you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, what are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, nothing. Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dark Magician Donpapa!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Führer Taiman, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There is information that the Great Goblin Tarobo
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.67,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of Champon Kingdom \Nis going to open up the country!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to use this opportunity \Nto usurp the Champon Kingdom for ourselves! {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.95,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! I have just a secret plan for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.63,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I have a huge variety of alcoholic beverages, including beer, wine, whiskey, and more!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.14,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own reserve for the night— \NI mean, my secret plan! {?? no idea what's that yozaku}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain clouds?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain is set to only come every Wednesday!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.58,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! This is a pain! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.79,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Smoking One \Nthat's spewing out rain clouds!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.22,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured out the mechanism here!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain keeps picking up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!\NHow very strange! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta hurry! \NRun, boy, run! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a natural disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our weather schedule got twisted.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather schedule? \NWhat could that be?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For over a thousand years, \Nit's been up to the Smoking One
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.66,0:18:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide whether it's going \Nto rain or shine in our kingdom today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain or shine? \NNow that's silly.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.61,0:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, what happened to Tarobo, \Nthe Great Goblin of the Smoking One?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, last I heard he was heading \Nto his son's Shichigosan Ceremony.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch an emergency party \Nto inspect the Smoking One.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At once!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.39,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My word... \NLeaving the weather to a goblin! {/tengu}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird island!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If we incorporated it into Japan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be nothing to gain from it! {/merit}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.70,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The real fun starts now! Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.08,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NKeep the booze flowing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.31,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Embrace this special \Ndrunken medicine from Donpapa!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to go back to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.57,0:20:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, not only will Claude not get better—\Nhe’s gonna end up one of those crazies!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.20,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Booze?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this stuff is good!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.67,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, teachers?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takamaru?  \NSchool’s out for the day!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.01,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.98,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, you drink too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink, drink!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.81,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Terrible! \NIsn't it alcohol?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol running from the tap—\Nwhere else would you find that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go to the castle and get drunk! {??? nc what's that shiro}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.59,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I'll take his son hostage and use him to blackmail the King of Champon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.50,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the grownups on the island drunk off their heads, this kingdom’s as good as ours!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Papa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dat thing you's gnawing \Nlookin' mighty tasty to me! {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.60,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind lendin' dat toy to we's?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're in trouble, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our toys's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.56,0:22:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the rush, Takamaru? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.57,0:22:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta see this!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.59,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Toys!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.75,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.67,0:22:39.60,Top,,0,0,0,,You don't need a special cause to drink... {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.60,0:22:40.22,Top,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H370070&}Hey, father! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.84,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh! Al, drink with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.84,0:22:43.45,Top,,0,0,0,,Is that your son?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.45,0:22:46.24,Top,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a secretary to Japan's Foreign— {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.25,0:22:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, head coach! Zugai-sama! {?????? nc what's that niwagan, no such name in my notes}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.19,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...\NYour highness! King! {??????? same}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.51,0:23:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't count on them...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.50,0:23:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter if the grownups can't help us. \NWe'll just have to do it on our own.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.37,0:23:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn! They'll pay \Nfor taking away my toys!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.73,0:24:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... It looks way bigger up close! {/when you come under it}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.81,0:25:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 400 meters high. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.73,0:25:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've no choice but to climb it!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:16.02,0:25:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.27,0:25:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep climbing it like that, you won't make it to the top even in three days!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.92,0:25:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai-dono? \NWhat's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.47,0:25:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the big idea, \Nmaking us laugh now of all times?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.39,0:25:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Smoking One is full of secret tunnels? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.22,0:25:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your deal, Mirai? \NWhy do we have to bring along a turtle shell?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.85,0:25:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to begin.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.22,0:25:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This sound...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.69,0:25:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like right before \Nthe Smoking One starts farting and peeing.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.27,0:25:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, place that shell on the hole.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.03,0:25:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.58,0:25:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We don't have much time!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.30,0:25:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.14,0:26:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now get inside! {to crouch; to squat; to cower}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.48,0:26:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:10.65,0:26:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:14.26,0:26:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, a hot spring?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:15.87,0:26:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a geyser.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.48,0:26:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Geyser, is that... \NLike a hot spring that erupts over time?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.23,0:26:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NAnd it'll carry us to the top!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.36,0:26:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This sound...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.88,0:26:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what the Smoking One's \Nfart and pee really are?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.25,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibo Takamaru! \NYumega Al Zaemon!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.68,0:26:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibo Takamaru! Yumega Al Zaemon! \NAre you safe?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.43,0:26:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It separated us?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:56.71,0:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mirai-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.60,0:27:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.30,0:27:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Did your friends come to save you?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.24,0:27:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.82,0:27:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt, goddammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:07.36,0:27:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Al! Al! Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.27,0:27:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru, help me! Takamaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:15.22,0:27:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! \NWhat courageous children!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.35,0:27:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic in comparison!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.96,0:27:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all the city kids like that? {kinda confirms my version of tokaemon}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:23.94,0:27:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:25.87,0:27:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.11,0:27:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, let's reward those kids appropriately for their courage. {https://jisho.org/word/%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E3%81%8C%E3%82%8B}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:44.35,0:27:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of Donpapa's three minions, Ninja Gorgeous.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.21,0:27:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as it pains me, \NI'll have to take your life, little girl! {young girl; lass; adolescent female(​oft. used derog. or teasingly)}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:51.98,0:27:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ninja" means someone who is discreet. {actually "shinobu" - just japanese word for "ninja"}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:54.07,0:27:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a fool introduces himself before a fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.63,0:27:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not a little girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:58.66,0:28:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.60,0:28:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can block my sword \Nwith your arm—I'm impressed!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.76,0:28:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A ninja needs not flashy decorations.\NDon't they hinder your movements? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.17,0:28:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me your concern!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.85,0:28:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unnecessary showing-off! \NUnsteady stance! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:24.45,0:28:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And stupid useless hat!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:26.40,0:28:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.90,0:28:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it—you've done it! \NLook, I won't show you any mercy now!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:31.84,0:28:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloning technique!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.46,0:28:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NWhy won't you attack?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:42.25,0:28:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a showy technique \Nis just a waste of effort. {/tiring}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:45.51,0:28:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Showy technique?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.68,0:28:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You broad!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:49.06,0:28:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the cloning technique is only effective if the enemy is actively trying to attack you.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.92,0:28:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just wait it out, \Nyou can't do anything to me. {watchful waiting; careful supervision}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:59.26,0:29:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:06.02,0:29:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Tired already?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:11.07,0:29:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can't support that many of them {/the number of clones decreased}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:19.07,0:29:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.72,0:29:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:22.05,0:29:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! Don't you know \Nit hurts, you little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:26.67,0:29:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate those who call me a little girl \Nor a child the most! You'll pay for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:31.96,0:29:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! No, please wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.97,0:29:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:39.42,0:29:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreigners can't become ninjas!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:41.97,0:29:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.02,0:29:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're eating too much meat!  {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.82,0:29:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.24,0:29:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd need to eat more small fish!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:48.19,0:29:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.98,0:29:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.49,0:29:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you won't be able \Nto save your friends anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:55.52,0:29:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.03,0:30:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad for a cretin.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.58,0:30:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Take this as a lesson \Nand never use your powers for evil again!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.10,0:30:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth! I'm not taking orders from a stupid little girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.30,0:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I was in the wrong! \NForgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:33.27,0:30:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.59,0:30:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru! Mirai!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:41.11,0:30:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamaru! Mirai!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.15,0:30:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, these two... \NWhere in the world did they go?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.32,0:30:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can feel lonely when left for so... {helpless; forlorn; hopeless; unpromising; lonely; discouraging; disheartening}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.35,0:30:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:53.24,0:30:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A pile of trash?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.93,0:31:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, bowy! Whau down'd wou bway wid be?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.56,0:31:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.27,0:31:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
